#Installation:
1. First install Node JS.
2. Run this command in cmd to install Angular "npm install -g @angular/cli".
3. Open Powershell as admin and run this command to ignore upcoming problem "powershell Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned".
4. Now open your project in VS Code and open terminal.
5. Now use this command to create a new Angular app "ng new your-project-name --no-standalone".

Note: --no-standalone command help to download all important resource for Angular.

#Create New Component:
1. Run this command in VS Code terminal "ng g c component-name".